Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.98,0:00:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Conectando suprimento de partículas Heigus.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.19,0:00:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Emissor ativo.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.53,0:00:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Solução de disparo alcançada.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.27,0:00:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Emissor de Raios Gravitônicos...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.48,0:00:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Disparando.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.59,0:00:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Emissão bem-sucedida.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.45,0:00:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Todas as matérias dentro de 100 quilômetros\Ndo eixo de emissão foram aniquiladas.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.13,0:00:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Comandante?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.42,0:00:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnífico.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.18,0:00:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Agradeço... você...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.38,0:00:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Potência impressionante.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.97,0:00:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim. É mais poderosa do que projetado.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.39,0:00:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,O experimento acabou.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.36,0:01:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Numi{**-chan}, corte a conexão\Ncom a partícula Heigus.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.03,0:01:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.37,0:01:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Capitã!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.11,0:01:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.54,0:01:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Numi{**-chan}, o que aconteceu?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.33,0:01:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Não consigo cortar a conexão\Ncom a linha de suprimento de Higgs.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.24,0:01:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,O que?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.34,0:01:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,O emissor não está respondendo\Nsus comandos.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.75,0:01:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Também continua se alimentando\Nautomaticamente da partícula de Higgs.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.09,0:01:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}{\r}Mas...
