Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.16,0:21:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nave de transporte, responda. Responda, nave de transporte.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.87,0:21:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nave falando.\NPodemos ouvi-lo bem e claro.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.62,0:21:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Aterrissamos na água.\NEverybody está bem.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.54,0:22:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Estávamos admirando a paisagem.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.29,0:22:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Parece ótimo. Estou um pouco invejoso.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.67,0:22:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Sim, esse lugar é basicamente parad—
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.14,0:22:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,O que houve?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.97,0:22:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Responda!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.68,0:22:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,O que houve?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.39,0:22:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.35,0:22:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Responda!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.27,0:22:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Base principal, falando do navio de transporte!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.15,0:22:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Temos uma emergência!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.86,0:22:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Gaun—
